* Wellman, Judith. &quot;Grassroots Reform in the Burned-over District of Upstate New York: Religion, Abolitionism, and Democracy&quot; (Routledge, 2014).
* Highly detailed scholarly synthesis.
* Intellectual history of Whigs and Democrats.

